data.name: IncompatibleEmbeddingGenerator
data.value: Embedding generator '{0}' is incompatible with the required input and output types. The property input type must be '{1}', and the output type must be '{2}'.

data.name: IncompatibleEmbeddingGeneratorWasConfiguredForInputType
data.value: An input of type '{0}' was provided, but an incompatible embedding generator of type '{1}' was configured.

data.name: NoEmbeddingGeneratorWasConfiguredForSearch
data.value: 'SearchAsync' requires an embedding generator to be configured. To pass an embedding directly, use 'SearchEmbeddingAsync', otherwise configure an embedding generator with your vector store connector.

data.name: NonEmbeddingVectorPropertyWithoutEmbeddingGenerator
data.value: Property '{0}' has non-Embedding type '{1}', but no embedding generator is configured.

data.name: EmbeddingTypePassedToSearchAsync
data.value: 'SearchAsync' performs embedding generation, and does not accept Embedding types directly. To search for an Embedding directly, use 'SearchEmbeddingAsync'.

data.name: EmbeddingPropertyTypeIncompatibleWithEmbeddingGenerator
data.value: Property '{0}' has embedding type '{1}', but an embedding generator is configured on the property. Remove the embedding generator or change the property's .NET type to a non-embedding input type to the generator (e.g. string).

data.name: IncludeVectorsNotSupportedWithEmbeddingGeneration
data.value: When an embedding generator is configured, `Include Vectors` cannot be enabled.

data.name: EmbeddingGeneratorWithInvalidEmbeddingType
data.value: An embedding generator was configured on property '{0}', but output embedding type '{1}' isn't supported by the connector.
